Commands
Development (unchanged)
cd VMA-frontend
npm run desktop

Build the installer
cd VMA-frontend
$env:CSC_IDENTITY_AUTO_DISCOVERY="false"
npm run build:installer
Output: VMA-frontend/dist/Voice Mode Agent Setup 0.1.0.exe (~133 MB)

What end users do
Run Voice Mode Agent Setup 0.1.0.exe
Choose install location → Install
Launch "Voice Mode Agent" from Start Menu or Desktop
App auto-starts the backend, waits for it, then shows the UI — no Python or Node needed
